snippet.title: Floor Plan 2: Backside Story - Official Announce Trailer | Upload VR Showcase 2023
snippet.description: Check out the announcement trailer for Floor Plan 2: Backside Story, featuring more floors and more puzzles. Floor Plan 2: Backside Story will be available on Meta Quest and Steam VR on June 22, 2023.
